title: ICL Icon Extractor 5.12 (Local install + Portable)
description:
**************************************************
ICL Icon Extractor 5.12 (Local install + Portable)
**************************************************

Icon Extractor for Windows extracts icons from your files, folders and Internet locations in seconds!

With ICL-Icon Extractor 5.12 you can:

- Quickly and efficiently scan files, folders or even entire drives for icon images
- Extract icon images from .ico, .cur, .ani, .exe, .icl, .dll, .scr, .il, .nil, .ocx, .vbx, .dpl, .bpl and other libraries
- Import .bmp, .jpg, .png, .gif, .wmf images into icon collections
- Create and manage .icl icon libraries
- Store found icons in special .icc icon collection format with icon source information
- Export icons to .ico, .png and .bmp files
- Copy icon images to clipboard
- Delete duplicate icons from collections
- Sort icons inside collections
- Split icon libraries into individual icon files
- Export any standard Windows icon (including Windows Vista icons) for future reuse
- Customize standard Windows icons
- Rebuild and repair the icon cache

System requirements: Windows 2000/XP/Vista/7/8/10

Homepage http://www.iconempire.com/icl-icon-extractor
